Interface ImageService

All Superinterfaces:
BaseService, PropertyNameConvertor<ImageView>, ViewService<ImageView>
public interface ImageService
    
extends BaseService, ViewService<ImageView>



This Interface describes the methods required to access and add details
of the images stored in the PiMS database.

findLatestImages


java.util.Collection<ImageView> findLatestImages(BusinessCriteria criteria)
                                                 throws BusinessException



    
Gets the latest images available for a plate. If no images have
    been taken, or the plate barcode is invalid, null is returned.
    

    

    

    

    

    

    

    

        
Parameters:

imageType - The type of image requested (High
        resolution, Medium Resolution, Composite, Thumbnail)
